64
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:06,740
But another reason why I'm going to buy them is because the skew is expensive.

65
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:11,840
So if I'm directional, and there's skew in my direction,

66
00:05:12,420 --> 00:05:15,240
